&lt;p&gt;This is a role with a significant runway. As you prove you can stand up and scale new business lines, the natural path is toward broader general management or product leadership - owning larger swaths of the business over time. If you want to operate at the center of a high-growth consumer business and work with a fast moving AI-native team, this is it.&lt;/p&gt;
