&lt;li&gt;Identify and establish the GTM and distribution partnerships needed to launch and scale new business lines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the connective tissue across product, product marketing, sales, engineering, operations, and partnerships - removing blockers, driving alignment, and keeping every function pulling toward the same outcome.&lt;/li&gt;
