&lt;li&gt;Partner with Workforce Management and Finance on headcount planning, cost modeling, and productivity benchmarking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI tools including Claude to accelerate analysis, automate recurring reporting, and prototype data solutions rapidly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain structured, documented analytical frameworks that can scale as the team grows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
