&lt;li&gt;New Product Launch Experience: Demonstrated experience leading paid marketing for new product launches or new business lines, ideally more than once.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic Judgment: You make sound calls without needing to escalate every decision. You know which trade-offs matter, which tests are worth running, and when to kill something.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic &amp;amp; Hands-On: You are equally excited by high-level strategy and the in-the-weeds work of building, testing, and shipping. You don&#39;t want a team to manage. You want to do the work.&lt;/li&gt;
